data.title: Damian Gerard Moloney Death Notice - Melbourne, Victoria
data.meta_description: MOLONEYDamian Gerard 28/8/1960 - 28/12/2021 Dearly loved son of the late Miriam and Jack Moloney. Cherished brotherof Mary, Carmel, Therese (Tess) and her partner Ian. Much loved husband of Veronique. Special uncle of Larrisa, Brendan and Sabrina. Reunited now with Mum, Dad and Uncle Pat. Rest in peace, our darling man. Ar dheis DÃ© go raibh a anam dlis (May his faithful soul be on the right hand of God) MOLONEYDamian Gerard Damian, my husband and my best friend. At your best, you were the best. We have loved each other in good times and in bad, in sickness and in health - love was always there, first and foremost. I love you and honour you for the person that you are. May you be at peace with God. Until we meet again my love, Veronique MOLONEYDamian Gerard Damian had an easy-goingand fun-loving personality that he shared with those closest to him.
